No. My mother did it, too.
It was great.

48
00:03:36,170 --> 00:03:38,026
In Vermont, we made
our own ice cream.

49
00:03:38,146 --> 00:03:40,014
It was a pain in the ass.

50
00:03:46,206 --> 00:03:48,230
Everyone breaks Popsicles in half.

51
00:03:49,029 --> 00:03:49,965
So?

52
00:03:50,085 --> 00:03:52,035
You can do it all year'round.

53
00:03:54,146 --> 00:03:56,865
